Look at the Data

So clearly there is a lot going on in Tennis serve data!
  • Position
    • Time, x, y, z coordinates
  • Speed
    • Speed on impact, speed throughout the serve
  • Curvature
    • Spin on the ball, Wind effects
  • Location
    • Single serve, Serve cluster
